  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eIn the heart of Ermionida, Greece, a former machinery workshop has been given a vibrant new identity as a dynamic and contemporary living space. \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/C_0Zb4ToE4e/?img_index=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eApartment V\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, a project by Anastasia Naki of \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/naki.atelier/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNaki Atelier\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, breathes new life into a once-industrial setting, integrating modern design elements while paying homage to its past.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573558\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573558\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-2-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern building entrance featuring a red-framed grid of glass blocks and a red door, set against light-colored steps and a smooth floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-2-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-2-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSpanning 807 square feet, the residence is strategically designed to optimize natural light. A wall of glass blocks surround the front entrance allowing light to enter the space while also prioritizing privacy. With only one external-facing facade, the architectural team prioritized its design to flood the interior with daylight, enhancing both ambiance and energy efficiency.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573559\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573559\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-3-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room with a green sofa, yellow curtain, orange wireframe magazine holder, and a glass block window allowing light to filter in.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-3-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-3-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-3-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-3-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-3.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573560\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573560\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-4-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with green sofa, glass coffee table, and red open staircase. Yellow curtains hang by a large window. Walls are white with geometric patterns. A small lamp sits on the table.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-4-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe layout is thoughtfully structured, dividing the home into two primary zones. The private section, containing two bedrooms and a bathroom, is accessible via a corridor that extends from the kitchen. Meanwhile, the public area of the apartment is an expansive, open-plan living area that combines various functions without compromising comfort or aesthetic appeal.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573561\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573561\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-5-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Living area features a TV on a stand, wall-mounted shelves with books and plants, a yellow curtain, and a kitchen with wooden cabinets and blue backsplash. Red door on the left.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-5-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573562\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573562\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-6-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with blue tiled backsplash, wooden cabinets, and a black marble countertop. Stools are at a breakfast bar, and various kitchen items are on shelves and the counter.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-6-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA defining feature of the renovation is a suspended steel loft – in a cherry red hue that is seen throughout the space – which serves multiple purposes. Hovering above the kitchen and dining space, this mezzanine area acts as an additional relaxation zone while simultaneously shaping the perception of height in the room. The elevated structure provides a sense of intimacy, counterbalancing the generous 14-foot-high ceilings. By incorporating this level, the design maintains an open connection between different parts of the apartment while ensuring a warm and inviting atmosphere.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573563\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573563\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-7-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Person in motion on a small loft with red railings, beside a bed and a framed picture. Bright, minimalist interior with white walls.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-7-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/