px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe material selection reflects both the industrial history of the space and a bold contemporary vision. A red steel framework anchors the design, echoing the building’s original function, while stainless steel custom-made furniture reinforces the industrial aesthetic. To balance these raw, robust elements, the interior features Tinos green marble, bold-hued tiles, thick textiles, and raw birch plywood – each adding texture and warmth to the space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573566\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573566\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-10-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom with an orange vanity, white sink, large mirror, and hanging towel. Walls are tiled in orange and white.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-10-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-10-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-10-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-10-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573567\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573567\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/Apartment-V-Greece-Naki-Atelier-11-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A partially open door reveals a bedroom with a bed and a spherical hanging light. A plant with large leaves is visible in the foreground.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://